page.title: 04EMPLOYMENT CHARACTERISTICS 2
page.content: although these tend to be doctors,pharmacists and dentists.3% of the sample are university lecturers. I would consider that this is about right for our block of land as Lymm is considered as a dormitory village for the surrounding cities and towns,and so would have a low unemployment rate,and a low retirement rate. Most of the housing in this block is largely privately owned with very few council owned properties.Most houses tend to be large semi-detached buildings many years old or newer detached houses in a small built up area,showing that the Lymm area is a rural area of wealthy people.
